com.hedera.hashgraph.sdk

Interface HederaThrowable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HederaNetworkException, HederaPrecheckStatusException, HederaReceiptStatusException, HederaRecordStatusException, HederaStatusException, MaxQueryPaymentExceededException

    public interface HederaThrowable
    Closed set of exception types thrown by this SDK; where HederaThrowable is passed to a callback, it is one of these types:
    • HederaStatusException
    • HederaNetworkException
    • MaxQueryPaymentExceededException
      • (thrown for queries)
